ence\nand the unusually slow rise of the light curve of the second 2008 outburst.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2010 21:05:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2010 00:14:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2010 17:20:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-01-21"}
